#~ "Fortunately the Nitrokey Start supports multiple curves, namely NIST, "
#~ "SECG and Curve25519. In what follows we will use Curve25519 and Ed25519 "
#~ "that is based upon this, both of which have a good reputation and are "
#~ "considered to be secure. `This article <https://arstechnica.com/"
#~ "information-technology/2013/10/a-relatively-easy-to-understand-primer-on-"
